<pc>、</pc>
<num value="3">三</num>佛 齊國王<pc>，</pc>給賜鞍馬<pc>、</pc>衣帶<pc>、</pc>銀器<pc>。</pc>賜使人宴於懷遠驛<pc>。</pc>淳熙<measure quantity="5" unit="years">
