<pc>，</pc>再來貢<pc>。</pc>景定<measure quantity="3" unit="years">
<num value="3">三</num>年</measure>
<measure quantity="6" unit="months">
<num value="6">六</num>月</measure>
<pc>，</pc>日煚上表貢獻<pc>，</pc>乞授其位於其子陳威晃<pc>。</pc>鹹淳元年<measure quantity="2" unit="months">
<num value="2">二</num>月</measure>
